- **microbiome-metabolome-subtyping** (ANALYSIS): Cluster stability v2 APPROVED — 2 robust CD subtypes confirmed (k=2, silhouette 0.344, bootstrap Jaccard 0.96-0.98, ARI=0.919). Biological validation reviewed: subtypes capture novel biology not explained by Montreal (p>0.3). Metabolite annotation gap (0.7%) documented as blind_spot, NOT a blocker. Added label: promising. PM task #1236 to proceed with cross-cohort (#852) and clinical relevance via HMP2 medication data (#851). Bile acid features (LCA, DCA, UDCA, CDCA) approved for check among annotated features. Tan et al. cross-validation deferred to cross-cohort phase.
